## About The Project

This project is a recreation of the Premier Models landing page using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

I originally started building this project while learning frontend development but left it incomplete. Recently, I revisited the project and completed it by improving the design, responsiveness, animations, and overall structure.

The website is fully responsive and works across mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

## Features

* Fully Responsive Design
* Mobile First Approach
* Hero Section
* Infinite Image Marquee
* Circular Text Animation
* Dynamic Alphabet Navigation
* Fashion Updates Section
* Blog Section
* Infinite Text Marquee
* Responsive Footer
* Dynamic Content Rendering

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)

## Concepts Used

* Flexbox
* CSS Grid
* Media Queries
* CSS Animations
* DOM Manipulation
* Event Handling
* Template Literals
* Array Methods
* Responsive Layout Design

